"ShaneRosalieRampEventMarried": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP Current Shane married#Wait, Rosalie?!$10 #$b# Gus' niece, Rosalie?! Rosa is coming back?!$10 #$b# $y 'I thought you didn't grow up here?_I didn't... #$b# _Wait you know her?_Yeah!$h #$b# Well, I used to..._Should I be worried?_No, no! I promise, she's not an ex or anything like that!$h' #$b# It's... a long story...$3 #$b# I'll tell you later... promise.$6",


