"ShaneRosalieArrivalCTMarried2": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP Current Shane married#Sorry I haven't been talking much lately, @. #$b# I think I'm just grappling with the idea that Rosa is back in Pelican Town. #$b# Rosa and I used to hang out when we were kids, in the summers when I'd stay with Marnie.$h #$b# Don't freak out, but she was actually my first kiss!$h #$e# Don't make a big deal about it, okay? It's ancient history, promise.$4",
"ShaneRosalieArrivalCTMarried3": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP Current Shane married#I didn't expect Rosa to be in my therapy group. #$b# We didn't talk...",


//CLICK DATA
"ShaneRadioClickVOTV": "It looks like Shane listens to The Voice of The Valley when he wakes up.",


//ROSALIE HEART EVENT CTS//

"Shane.RosalieGeorgeWCCT": "$query PLAYER_HAS_SEEN_EVENT Current 3910975#George is lucky I wasn't out there. I hope he apologizes properly to Rosa.$5|I didn't know what was going on until I saw Rosa come in...$3 #$b#Not that me being there would have made a difference...$2",

"Shane.RosalieVOTVJobEventCT":"$query PLAYER_HAS_SEEN_EVENT Current {{ModId}}_RosaliesRibbonEventPost#Yeah, Rosa told me about her new gig. I'm happy for her.$6|It's nice to know I'm the only one in town who still has a radio, I guess. #$e# I use it as an alarm clock. It's better than some annoying tone.$11",

"Shane.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "$query PLAYER_HAS_SEEN_EVENT Current {{ModId}}_ShaneRosalieDreamsAndDisastersEvent#Rosa put up with her lazy ex's excuses and broken logic for thirteen years.$5 #$b# I'm amazed she has that much patience with the luck she's been given.$11 #$b# Then again, she has me as an excuse for a best friend...$3 #$b# The difference is, if I had a wife like her, and she was suffering as much as Rosa is,$3 #$b# I swear to Yoba, I wouldn't drag her down to my level like her leech of an ex husband. No matter how bad things got.$5 #$b# I know I wouldn't want Jas to be with someone like that. No one deserves to be that unhappy.$11 #$e# 'A wife like her'?! I said 'If I had a wife!' Like, in general!!$10 #$b# Don't twist my words, @!$11|I'll be honest... I figured that's what happened...$2 #$b# Last I heard about Rosa, seven years ago, she got married. So, her coming here alone... it wasn't rocket science.$3 #$e# I think it would be pretty messed up to be happy someone's marriage is ending.$3 #$b# But if the guy was burdening her more than he was helping her, then yeah, I'm glad. He doesn't deserve her.$5",
"Shane.RosalieRadioEventCT": "$query PLAYER_HAS_SEEN_EVENT Current {{ModId}}_RosaliesRibbonEventPost#I'm glad she pulled you in for an interview instead of me. I probably would have cursed or said something inapproprite on the air, then what?$1|So, @, are you enjoying your seven seconds of fame? #$b# I'm not jealous, I'm honestly glad it wasn't me.$1",

//Shane x Rosalie Route CTs//

//Location Talk//

"ShanexRosalieBFF.Saloon1": "Hey, @! Can you tell Rosa that the whole 'older than you' thing only works when you're kids?$1",
"ShanexRosalieBFF.Saloon2": "Rosa honestly makes me forget why I used to come here in the first place.$6 #$b# At least... for a while...$2",
"ShanexRosalieBFF.Saloon3": "How's your arm doing, Rosa?$6 #$e# You better not be pushing yourself too hard.",
"ShanexRosalieBFF.Saloon4": "%Shane is busy focusing on a story Rosalie's telling.",
 
"Shane_Forest_93_24": "$query PLAYER_HAS_SEEN_EVENT stardewaly.rosalie_ShaneRosalieCandleEvent#Shane is busy.|%Shane is paying attention to Rosalie's story.",



//BUS EVENT CT//
"Shane.TherapyCT": "How's therapy going? #$b# It's been... interesting...$3.",
"Shane.TherapyCT1": "Rosalie tried talking to me in group therapy today. #$b# I mean, I guess that's... nice?$s",


//ROSALIE'S RIBBON CT//

"Shane.RosaliesRibbonCT": "Hey, @. Sorry for being a bit stand off-ish about Jas' ribbon. #$b# I really appreciate you getting it for her.",
"Shane.RosaliesRibbonCT2": "Marnie told you Rosalie and I have history, huh? #$b# Yeah, we used to hang out in the summers as kids when my parents would dump me here. It's really not that deep.$3 #$e#. What was she like as a kid? I... Um... I don't really remember...$3",

//SNEEZE EVENT CT//
"Shane.RosalieSneezeEventCT1": "Not you too, @!$5 #$b# Why can't I just walk a friend home without it 'meaning' something?!$11 #$e# Yeah, we talked a lot yesterday, and shared some laughs. #$b# She's just... easy to talk to, okay?$3",
"Shane.RosalieSneezeEventCT2": "I won't lie, seeing Rosa fall like that... It really shows you how much she puts up with every day.$2 #$b# She's a lot stronger than me, that's for sure.",

//CHILDHOOD TALK WITH JAS CT//
"Shane.ShaneRosalieChildhoodTalkJasCT1": "I hate to say it, but Dr Harvey was right. #$b# It doesn't matter how much you try to hide it, kids can tell when something's wrong.$2 #$e# I was always able to tell when my parents were struggling financially. #$b# It didn't surprise me when I found out my dad gambled away my tuition for gridball camp.$11 #$b# I met Rosa that summer, but I think I have the right to hold a grudge.$11",
"Shane.ShaneRosalieChildhoodTalkJasCT2": "Don't tell Rosa I said this, but I think the reason she married so young is because she wanted to get out of the house. #$b# She loves her family, and people in town said she was 'very mature for her age', but that's because she was forced to grow up too fast. #$e# I think we clicked because I understood what it was like to be 'too young' to do anything, then be expected to act like an adult...$11 #$e# I hope Jas doesn't ever have to know what it was like growing up feeling that way...$2",

//SHANE'S LOW DAY CT//

"Shane.ShaneRosalieLowDayCT": "It's weird how Rosa and I hadn't talked for twenty years, and now that we're friends again, it feels like no time has passed.$6 #$b# Sure, we're older and I've lost my good looks, but she's still Rosa.$1",
"Shane.ShaneRosalieLowDayCT2": "I'm glad that Rosa and I are able to take care of each other. We don't feel the need to hide anything just to make the other more comfortable. #$e# I do worry she isn't taking care of herself though...$2",
"Shane.ShaneRosalieLowDayCT3": "Hey, don't take offence to Rosa saying I'm her best friend. #$b# Rosa and I have history, we've just known each other for longer. #$b# You're still the person who saved my life. No one's taking that away from you.$1 #$e# I can have more than one best friend, calm down.$1",
"Shane.ShaneRosalieLowDayCT4": "For as long as I've known her, Rosa has been great with animals. #$b# She used to tell me that animals don't judge you for being different or being too much...$2 #$b# But Charlie is probably the one animal on earth who hates her. I guess we can't all be perfect.$1 #$e# She's trying though. Rosa I mean, Charlie not so much.$1 #$e# Don't worry, I won't let Rosa get hurt. It's actually kind of cute how much she's trying.$6",
    
//DREAMS AND DISASTERS CT//

"Shane.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT1": "Can you believe there are people out there who just... live to take the joy out of people?$11 #$b# I mean, you worked for Joja, you know what it's like.$3 #$e# No one deserves to be treated that way by anyone. Especially by someone you love.$5",
"Shane.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT2": "It sucks that Rosa and I didn't get to achieve our dreams. But I think we're doing alright.$6 #$e#",
"Shane.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT3": "What kind of man hurts the woman he claims to love? I can't stand the fact people like that exist. #$e# I'll never understand why Rosa didn't leave when he did, but I guess it's the kind of person she is...$2 #$e# I hope she knows now that she deserves better than that.",

//SLEEP OVER CT//

"Shane.RosalieShaneSleepoverCT1": "Thanks for not telling anyone about me sleeping over. #$b# I trust you with my life, @. #$b# But the last thing Rosa needs is for people to gossip about her. #$e# I could care less about what people say about me, but Rosa doesn't deserve that.$2",
"Shane.RosalieShaneSleepoverCT2": "Rosa deserves a chance at happiness. #$b# I don't want to screw that up for her. #$e# Her ex husband was her best friend in high school, and he treated her like garbage. #$b# I don't want to be that guy.$3 #$e# I just... want to be someone she can rely on.$2",
"Shane.RosalieShaneSleepoverCT3": "For the record, I slept *over* the blankets.$3 #$b# She may have put another on top of me in the night or something, I don't know.$3 #$e# That's all you're getting out of me. Now drop it.$5",

//Sand Castles With Jas CT//
  "Shane.SandCastlesWithJasCT1": "I don't know if Rosa is a witch, or Jas is plotting something, but I swear, Jas is always on her best behaviour when Rosa is around.$1",
  "Shane.SandCastlesWithJasCT2": "I know what people are saying, Jas included, but Rosa and I are just friends. #$b# Not like she'd be interested in me, right?$2 #$e# Me? Interested in Rosa?$10 #$b# I don't have to answer that.$1",
  "Shane.SandCastlesWithJasCT3": "Rosa's mentioned having a goddaughter. #$b# A friend of her's she met after she moved across the sea. #$b# Unlike Jas' parents, her friend is still around. #$e# I know Rosa worries she's not doing enough for her, but she can't exactly compare her experience to mine.$2 #$e# The kid's name? Rosalie.",
  "Shane.SandCastlesWithJasCT4": "I know Rosa said she doesn't want to be with anyone again, #$b# and I don't blame her after everything her ex put her through...$2 #$b# But... if she did...$2 #$b# ...$6 #$b# Buh, forget it.$3 #$e# We just have a good thing going as friends.$2 #$b# I don't want to mess that up by making things weird.$11",

//KITCHEN LOVE//

"Shane.RosalieKitchenLoveCT": "Urg... I don't know if I almost did something really stupid,#$b# Or almost did something really smart.$6 #$e# Um... I'd rather not talk about it...$3 #$e#",
"Shane.RosalieKitchenLoveCT2": "I don't know if you know what it's like feeling happy, then anxious thinking it's going to leave you...$2 #$b# I sometimes wonder if I rely on Rosa too much... #$b# Not that she's in charge of my emotions, I'd never do that.$2 #$b# But I don't know... if everything is just temporary... Why stick around?$11 #$b# I guess it would be selfish to want to keep that kind of light to yourself, huh?$2",

//TEASING CTs// (when they get closer)
"Shane.JasTeasing": "Jas has been obsessed with Rosa since you gave her the ribbon!$1 #$b# Here I thought I was her favourite person!$1 #$e$",

//SECOND FIRST KISS CT//
"Shane.RosalieShaneSecondFirstKissCT": "Sorry, @. I just need to be alone.$2 #$b# I'll be fine... eventually.$2 #$e# No, I don't want to talk about it... And Rosa is... fine... I think...$2 #$b# Just, go away, please...$11",


//CANDLE EVENT CT//

"Shane.RosaliexShane": "I thought I had to be perfect and healed to be worthy of someone like Rosa.$2 #$b# But by some miracle, she likes me flaws and all. I'm gonna keep trying to earn that.$6",
"Shane.RosaliexShane_oneday": "You don't think Rosa's gonna change her mind about me, do you?$2 #$e# I mean, it's not too late for her to take it back...$2",
"Shane.RosaliexShane_oneweek1": "Rosa and I try to keep our relationship outside of group therapy. If we have problems, we work on them together. #$b# Or she calls her sister to complain about me.$1 #$e# Apparently her sister is... more level headed than I remember her being.$11",
"Shane.RosaliexShane_oneweek2": "Rosa and Charlie still aren't getting along, but it's hilarious to see Rosa try.$6",
"Shane.RosaliexShane_oneweek3": "Rosa and I had a bit of an argument last night. #$e# Doesn't matter what it was about. But, it turns out we were just hungry.$1 #$e# I swear the world's problems would probably be solved over a pizza and beer.$1",
"Shane.RosaliexShane_twoweeks1": "$query !IS_COMMUNITY_CENTER_COMPLETE#Sam started calling me 'Farm Boy' at work all day.$11 #$b# I thought I was pissed, but when Rosa heard him call me that...$6 #$b# Sam looked like he saw the face of Yoba. She's great.$1|Don't get any ideas about calling me 'Farm Boy' now that Rosa and I are dating.$11 #$b# I may be pissed, but Rosa will likely bite your head off. She's great.$1",
"Shane.RosaliexShane_twoweeks2": "I took Rosa to a Tunnelers game the other day. Maybe not the most ideal date with the noise, but we both had fun!$1",
"Shane.RosaliexShane_fourweeks1": "Rosa's disability has really given me some perspective on things. Before going anywhere new, I have to check if the place is accessible cause I don't want her struggling.$3 #$b# The world really isn't made with people like her in mind.$11",
"Shane.RosaliexShane_fourweeks2": "I know Rosa loves her parents, but I can also see why she always felt she had to put up with more than she had to. #$e# I hope she doesn't feel like she doing the same with me now that we're dating...",
"Shane.RosaliexShane_eightweeks1": "$query !IS_COMMUNITY_CENTER_COMPLETE#I think I've gotten stronger from pushing Rosa around in her wheelchair. #$b# Today at work, I was able to lift a couple crates of oranges without any issues.|I think I've gotten stronger from pushing Rosa around in her wheelchair. #$b# The other day, I was able to lift a couple crates of milk without any issues.$1",
"Shane.RosaliexShane_eightweeks2": "I used to think my feelings for Rosa were just about nostalgia. #$b# But I didn't think I'd ever feel this strongly about anyone...$l",
"Shane.RosaliexShane_eightweeks3": "You know, I never thanked you properly for saving me that day on the cliffs...$3 #$b# If it weren't for you, I wouldn't have reconnected with Rosa, she and Jas wouldn't have met, and I wouldn't feel this... hopeful...$6 #$b# So, thank you, @.$6",
"Shane.RosaliexShane_eightweeks4": "I've been noticing lately Jas sometimes calls her “Auntie” Rosa. I'm still trying to figure out how I feel about that.$3 #$e# I haven't corrected her yet. But I probably should. I don't want to get her hopes up or make Rosa think I'm pressuring her to stick around...$2",

"Shane.RosaliexShane_oneyear1": "I love Rosa... and I know she's the one...$4$ #$b# But honestly, I think we're both happy with how things are now.$6 #$b# I don't want her sticking around and making her feel trapped just because a shell or piece of paper said so.$11 #$b# But if she said she wanted that again, I'd ask her faster than I could chug a pint of beer.$1 #$e# Plus the government gives you less money when you're married and disabled. Messed up, huh?$11 #$e# At least this way, Rosa and I have a clean break if she ever comes to her senses about me.$1",
"Shane.RosaliexShane_oneyear2": "You know, Marnie's told me for years that Jas would benefit from a 'mother figure'...$6 #$b# I'll admit, seeing Jas and Rosa together makes me think maybe she was right...$l",
"Shane.RosaliexShane_oneyear3": "I met Rosa's goddaughter last week after group therapy. She's younger than Jas but Rosa's good with her. #$e# She keeps saying she doesn't like or want kids but how she acts with them, it makes me wonder...$2 #$b# Nah! Can you imagine me and Rosa having kids?$1 #$e# Rosa would be a great mom, but I'd be a terrible dad!$1 #$e# I... didn't exactly have the best role model. So I'd only screw it up...$2",

//Dating Rosalie//
    "Shane.RosaliexShane1": "I never thought I'd find someone who could put up with me for longer than five minutes. I guess technically, I already did.$1",
    "Shane.RosaliexShane2": "It feels so surreal knowing that Rosa and I are dating.$6 #$b# I didn't think I'd ever feel this light again...$4",
    "Shane.RosaliexShane3": "I think Rosa and I have something really special... I just hope she feels the same way.$4",
    "Shane.RosaliexShane4": "Rosa said the other day that I'm more poetic than I give myself credit for. I thought that was a weird thing to say. But then the person running group therapy mentioned it too. #$b# 'I'm just a piece of soiled garbage flittering in the wind...'?#$b# 'Flittering'? Buh... I'm such an idiot.$11",
    "Shane.RosaliexShane5": "Rosa gets that it's exhausting to just exist sometimes. #$b# Yeah I have dark thoughts and so does Rosa, but on top of that, her pain takes away her energy. #$e# It can be hard to watch.$2",
    "Shane.RosaliexShane6": "Rosa is probably my first best friend since Jas' parents died... #$b# I... hope she sticks around...$4",
    "Shane.RosaliexShane7": "I know that Rosa looks younger than me, make no mistake, we're the same age!$h #$b# Well, she's technically older than me, but we were born in the same year.$1",
    "Shane.RosaliexShane8": "It feels so surreal knowing that Rosa and I are dating.$6 #$b# I didn't think I'd ever feel this light again...$4",
    "Shane.RosaliexShane9": "I understand what Rosa sees in me that makes her want to keep me around. #$e# But if someone like her can fall in love with me, I guess I'm not so bad.$1",



//Flare Up CT

    "Shane.Flareup_1": "I know Rosa seems like she's doing okay a lot of the time, #$b# She's not. She's just better at hiding it than most.$3 #$e#She's a good actress, but she's never had me fooled...$2",
    "Shane.Flareup_2": "I'm gonna go visit Rosa... I think she needs a friend.$2",




//WINTER MARKET IF SHANE X ROSALIE BECOMES A THING

"Shane.WinterMM.FirstYear1": "I think some time apart will be good for Rosa and I. #$b# I know I get on her nerves sometimes.$1",
"Shane.WinterMM.FirstYear2": "*sigh* It's too quiet...",
"Shane.WinterMM.FirstYear3": "Anytime I miss Rosa, I just remember that she's living her dream. #$b# I never got that chance, but I'm gonna support her like she always has with me.",
"Shane.WinterMM.FirstYear4": "In the summers, Rosa used to help me write essays to get a scholarship for Gridball camp. #$b# I wouldn't have Jas in my life if it weren't for Rosa.$6 #$b# The least I can do is wait for her.$6",



"Shane.WinterMM.1Year": "*sigh* Like seasonal depression wasn't enough...$2 #$e# I hope Rosa can get a job close by next time...$2",


"Shane.MermaidEventUpcoming": "I know Rosa never got to see me play any games, but I plan on being there every night to see her perform.$6 #$e# I know she worries about me when she's away...$2",


"Shane.MermaidEvent1": "Maybe I'm biased, but I think the mermaid show is better now that Rosa's in it.$6",

"Shane_RosalieTheMermaid.NightMarket1": "Jas really wanted to watch the Mermaid show, but she's still too young.",
"Shane_RosalieTheMermaid.NightMarket2.1": "Yup. I'm here again. Doing my due diligence as a supportive partner.$1 #$e# Besides, someone's gotta keep the creeps away.$11",
"Shane_RosalieTheMermaid.NightMarket2.2": "You'd think I'd be sick of listening to Rosa sing and her perform. But honestly, I haven't.$1 #$b# She's just... amazing... I can't believe she's my girlfriend...$4",
"Shane_RosalieTheMermaid.NightMarket2.3": "I never understood what Rosa meant when she said she liked 'seeing people be passionate, but watching her on stage, I get it now.$1 #$b# She's... mesmerizing...$4",
"Shane_RosalieTheMermaid.NightMarket2.4": "I'm surprised Harvey isn't here every night for the free coffee. #$e# Oh, I only know that 'cause Rosa told me she used to bring him coffee all the time.$1",
"Shane_RosalieTheMermaid.NightMarket2.5": "Maybe I'm biased, but I think the mermaid show is better now that Rosa's in it.$6",
"Shane_RosalieTheMermaid.NightMarket2.6": "I'm freezing out here, but I can't imagine how Rosa and the other mermaids are doing.$2 #$e# I'd bring her coffee but I read somewhere that it dries your voice.$2",


"Shane_RosalieTheMermaid.NightMarketDay3.1": "*sigh* Last night, then Rosa's gonna go back out on tour...$2 #$b# But I'm not trying to dwell on it, Rosa wouldn't want me to.$6",
"Shane_RosalieTheMermaid.NightMarketDay3.2": "Have you watched the Mermaid show yet? Rosa's killing it as always!$1 #$e# I still have no idea how someone like Rosa fell for someone like me.$4",
"Shane_RosalieTheMermaid.NightMarketDay3.3": "Rosa was having a bit of a flare up earlier, though she didn't say anything...$2 #$b# She's still okay to perform, but I hope I didn't push her too hard trying to catch up...$2 #$e# She'll be gone tomorrow anyway, so hopefully she'll be okay by the Feast of the Winter Star.$2 #$e# May have her in her wheelchair this year if she's stubbourn.$3",
"Shane_RosalieTheMermaid.NightMarketDay3.4": "Yeah, I've been here every night. So what? A guy can't just support the arts?$3 #$e# And yeah, I'm dating the mermaid. Don't make a big deal about it.$11",


"Shane.SpiritsEveMM": "Don't tell Rosa, but I only dressed up because it's her last day here. #$e# It'll be nice to have some space and quiet, but I'm gonna miss her a lot...$2",
"Shane.WinterStarMM": "It sucks that Rosa's only here for a day. But we get the other three seasons.$6",



//2 Hearts//
    "ShaneOnRosalie_2Hearts1": "Rosalie? She's Gus' niece, right? #$b# I don't know much about her.$3",

//4 Hearts//
    "ShaneOnRosalie_4Hearts1": "Rosalie seems... nice, I guess. #$b# I don't really know her that well.$s",

//6 Hearts//
    "ShaneOnRosalie_6Hearts1": "Rosalie tried talking to me in group therapy today. #$b# I mean, I guess that's... nice?$s",
    "ShaneOnRosalie_6Hearts4": "Rosa and I are getting pretty close. We spend almost every day together.$6 #$b# Last time I remember laughing so hard, we were kids.$h",

//8 Hearts//
    "ShaneOnRosalie_8Hearts1": "Rosa is probably the closest friend I've made in a long time.$6 #$b# Present company excluded$h",
    "ShaneOnRosalie_8Hearts2": "Rosa's been helping me a lot... #$b# I don't think I've ever had someone care about me like that before.$l",
    "ShaneOnRosalie_8Hearts3": "Rosa and Jas get along really well. #$b# Sometimes I think Jas sees Rosa as the mom she never had.$l",
           
        
//10 Hearts - Shane is Dating Player BUT NOT Rosalie//

"ShaneOnRosalie_10Hearts1": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP Current Shane married PLAYER_HEARTS Current stardewaly.rosalie_Rosalie 4#Rosa was thinking we could have a game night sometime. What do you think?$h",


















//*******MARNIE*******//


    "MarnieRosalieRamp": "A new ramp at the saloon? #$b# I wonder what happened to make them finally put one in!$h #$e# ...$3 #$e#%Marnie looks troubled by something.",
"MarnieRosalieArrivalCT1": "It's so nice that Rosa is back home. #$e# Huh? I said 'Rosalie', didnt I?",
"MarnieRosalieArrivalCT2": "Try to take it easy on Shane today... He hasn't been doing well lately...$s",
"MarnieRosalieArrivalCT3": "I hate arguing with Shane...$2 #$b# I love him, but I wish he wasn't so stubburn.$3 #$e#He's my sister's kid alright...",


//ROSALIES EVENT CTS//
"Marnie.RosalieGeorgeWCCT": "Shane's been quiet since what happened with George.$s #$b# He's always been protective of Rosa.",
"Marnie.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "*sigh* The poor, poor dear...$s #$b# Just when you think that she's been dealt an awful hand, it gets worse for her...$3 #$e# I hope people don't judge her too harshly. She's very brave to do that and keep a smile on her face.$s",


//ROSALIE X SHANE CTS//
"Marnie.RosaliesRibbonCT": "Thank you so much for talking to Rosalie about the ribbon. #$b# I'm sure she'll be wearing it for a long time and be thinking of you!$1",
    "Marnie.RosalieSneezeEventCT1": "It's hard seeing the little girl you watched grow up in so much pain...$s #$b# I was worried about her with Shane walking her home to the saloon,$s #$b# But last night was the first time in years Shane came home from the saloon without any alcohol in his system.$1 #$b# I haven't seen Shane smile so much in years.$1 #$e# I know Rosa has her struggles as well, but I think the two of them are really good for each other.$1 #$b# I hope they continue to be friends. #$e# Sometimes an old friend is exactly what you need to get through the tough times...$2",
    "Marnie.RosalieSneezeEventCT2": "I hope Rosa will come by again sometime. It was so nice having her back at the ranch despite the circumstances… #$b# Maybe I'll ask if she's allergic to something so we can prevent further sneezes.",
"Marnie.ShaneRosalieChildhoodTalkJasCT1": "I know it seems like Rosa and Shane are very different people, #$b# But they're actually more similar than you think. #$b# They were both shy children who had a talent they were known for by their parents, #$e# They were left alone a lot as kids.$2",
"Marnie.ShaneRosalieChildhoodTalkJasCT2": "I sometimes wonder if my sister had allowed Shane's half siblings into his life growing up if things would have turned out differently... #$b# Rosa loves her family, but it was clear she kept a lot of her troubles to herself growing up...$3 #$b# I'm glad that she and Shane are seeking therapy though. It seems to be working well for them.$1",
"Marnie.ShaneRosalieChildhoodTalkJasCT3": "You know, over the last twenty years, I always wondered what it would have been like if Rosa's family hadn't moved... #$b# Even though he got the scholarship the summer she left, Shane and Rosa still would have gone to the same high school, you know? #$b# I would have bet a year's worth of milk and eggs on him asking her to prom.$1 #$b# *sigh* It's unfortunate they had to grow up without each other... I'm sure it would have saved them a lot of heartbreak and trouble...$3",
"Marnie.ShaneRosalieLowDayCT": "Shane really had me worried there...$2 #$b# But I'm glad that he has friends like you and Rosa to depend on.",
"Marnie.RosalieShaneDreamsAndDisastersCT": "Shane used to love playing with Rosa as kids, I'm glad they found each other again as adults.",
"Marnie.RosalieShaneSleepoverCT": "I thought I heard Shane came home really early this morning...$2 #$b# He didn't say much other than to not say anything, and went right back to sleep...$2 #$e# I hope he didn't do anything he'll regret...$3",
"Marnie.SecondFirstKissCT1": "Shane's been quiet again lately... I'm really worried about him...$2 #$e# Rosa isn't answering my calls either... I wonder if something happened...$s",
"Marnie.SecondFirstKissCT2": "I haven't seen Shane this quiet since that last day Rosa was here...$2#$b# It's a strange sense of deja vu, but I called Gus and I asked if Rosa was moving...$2 #$b# He said that she hadn't talked about it recently, but I hope if she does leave, she says goodbye. #$e# Jas would be so heartbroken if Rosa left...$2",
  
"Marnie.RosaliexShane": "Shane and Rosa told me the good news last night! I'm so happy for them!$1 #$e# I've never seen Shane so happy.$1",
"Marnie.RosaliexShane_oneday": "I wonder how long it'll take for Shane and Rosa to tell Charlie about their relationship.$2",
"Marnie.RosaliexShane_oneweek": "I can tell that Shane feels a bit insecure about himself now that he and Rosalie are together. Like he's not doing enough for her.$3 #$b# I hope he doesn't let it interfere with their relationship.$2",
"Marnie.RosaliexShane_twoweeks": "I used to wonder what would have happened if Rosa hadn't moved.$2 #$b# But I suppose it doesn't matter now. They've found each other again at the right time.$1",
"Marnie.RosaliexShane_fourweeks": "Shane's been taking his role as Jas' godfather a bit more seriously lately. #$e# I wonder if Rosa has something to do with that.$1",
"Marnie.RosaliexShane_eightweeks": "Shane won't admit it but he is crazy about Rosa. #$b# It's amazing how much care he puts into making sure she's comfortable in ways she doesn't notice.$1",
"Marnie.RosaliexShane_oneyear": "I always hoped to see Shane married someday, but I understand why Rosa would be hesitant to be married again with all she's been through.$2 #$e# As long as Shane and Rosa are happy, I guess it doesn't matter if you don't have the fancy wedding.$1",

"Marnie.RosalieTheWinterMermaid": "We're all so proud and happy for Rosa on her getting the part.$1 #$b# We're all going to miss her, especially Shane, but they have the other three seasons to be together.$1 #$e# I'm so proud of Shane for being supportive of Rosa. Even if they're apart, he seems secure enough to trust her.$1",


    //Not triggered (yet?)

    "Marnie.SandCastlesWithJasCT1": "Jas refused to eat her broccoli the other night, but when Rosa came over for dinner, Jas made a big show of eating it all!$1 #$e# If Jas continues to behave when Rosa's around, I may need to consider asking her to move in!",
    "Marnie.SandCastlesWithJasCT2": "I hope Jas doesn't get her hopes up too high about Shane and Rosa becoming a couple...$2 #$e# It's not that I don't see it too, Shane and Rosalie have always been close, closer than most friends, #$b# But if it's really nothing more, I don't want to see Jas hurt.$2 #$e# Rumour has it that she had eyes for someone else before she and Shane began talking again.$2 #$b# It's entirely possible that hasn't changed.$3",
    "Marnie.SandCastlesWithJasCT3": "Shane and Rosa are both adults. I'm sure if they wanted to be more than friends, they would have said something. #$b# I know Rosa has been hurt by her ex, but she knows Shane would never hurt her like he did. #$e# I like to think that Rosa would feel comfortable coming to me too, I always loved her like a niece.$h #$e#",

    "Marnie.Flareup_1": "I don't know how Shane always seems to know when Rosa is hurting,$2#$b#Even when they were kids, they both would just... know.",
    "Marnie.Flareup_2": "Shane always worries about Rosa on days like this...$s #$e# I'm sure she's alright, but Shane left to check her.",




//*******JAS*********//

"JasRosalieArrivalCT": "Shane and Marnie have been fighting lately...$2",

//ROSALIES RIBBON EVENT CT//
"Jas.RosaliesRibbonCT": "Shane and Marnie stopped fighting, and I have a pretty ribbon!$h #$b# Thank you, @.",


//SNEEZE EVENT CT//
"Jas.RosalieSneezeEventCT": "Miss Rosa explained to me that her condition is like stubbing your toe, and your brain tells you you're hurt.$3 #$b# But her brain is wired different and tells her that she's hurt all the time.$3 #$e# It's kind of scary...$2",


//Childhood Talk With Jas//
"Jas.ShaneRosalieChildhoodTalkJasCT1": "I think it's funny that Uncle Shane and Miss Rosa have known each other since they were kids. #$e# Uncle Shane can try to deny it, but he was definitely in love with Miss Rosa!$1 #$e# I know Miss Rosa is an actress, but I bet that I can get her to admit if she loved Uncle Shane, too!$4",
"Jas.ShaneRosalieChildhoodTalkJasCT2": "I hope I'm as pretty as Miss Rosa when I grow up!$2",
"Jas.ShaneRosalieChildhoodTalkJasCT3": "I wonder if Uncle Shane was as much of a grump as he is now when he was a kid.$1 #$e# Do you think Uncle Shane and Miss Rosa would still be friends now if they hadn't met when they were kids...$3",

//SHANES LOW DAY//
"Jas.ShaneRosalieLowDayCT": "Shane seemed a little low energy today...$3 #$b# But I saw him later with Miss Rosa and he was smiling that goofy grin again! #$e# If there's anything that can brighten Uncle Shane's day, it's chickens and Miss Rosa.$1 #$e# Charlie would probably say otherwise though...$3",


"Jas.ShaneRosalieKitchenLoveCT": "Uncle Shane turned off Rosa's show really fast this morning...$3",

"Jas.SecondFirstKissCT1": "Uncle Shane's being sad again... But it's a different kind of sad...$2 #$e# I tried to ask Rosa to come over and cheer him up like she always does, but she told me she couldn't because of 'grown up stuff'.$2 #$e# I hope it's not my fault...$2",
"Jas.SecondFirstKissCT2": "I hope Miss Rosa isn't moving away again...$2",


    "Jas.RosaliexShane": "I take full credit for Uncle Shane and Rosa falling in love!$4",
    "Jas.RosaliexShane_oneday": "I hope Uncle Shane doesn't mind that I told Charlie already about him and Rosa.$1",
    "Jas.RosaliexShane_oneweek": "Rosa is so nice and so pretty and makes Uncle Shane so happy!#$e# I hope they stay together forever.$h",
    "Jas.RosaliexShane_twoweeks": "I asked Uncle Shane last week if we could dress up for next Spirit's Eve, and he said no.$3 #$b# But then Rosa said she wanted to do a couples costume and he said 'okay'! #$b# I wonder what else I could tell Rosa to ask Shane for!$1",
    "Jas.RosaliexShane_fourweeks": "I hope one day someone will look at me the way Shane looks at Rosa...$3",
    "Jas.RosaliexShane_eightweeks": "Auntie Rosa and Uncle Shane snore loud. It's like two bears hibernating in a cave!$1",
    "Jas.RosaliexShane_oneyear": "I asked Uncle Shane hasn't given Auntie Rosa a mermaid pendent so she could *really* be my Aunt, but he said that she'd probably say no.$3 #$b# Why doesn't Rosa want to be my Auntie?$2",

"Jas.RosalieTheWinterMermaidCT": "One day, Rosa's gonna show me her *real* mermaid tail!$1 #$b# It's not a coincidence she's playing a mermaid!$4",

//Not triggered CT//

"Jas.SandCastlesWithJasCT": "I knew Miss Rosa was a mermaid! I knew it!$h #$e# I'm glad Uncle Shane likes mermaids, too...$3 #$e# He says they're just friends, but he has a funny smile when she's around.$h #$e# If TV has taught me anything, it's true love!$4",


}
